org.batfish.datamodel.acl

Class CanonicalAcl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.acl.CanonicalAcl

  • public final class CanonicalAcl
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an ACL with all its dependencies for the purpose of detecting identical ACLs.

                    java.util.Set<java.lang.Integer> linesWithUndefinedRefs,
                    java.util.Set<java.lang.Integer> linesInCycles)
        Parameters:
        sanitizedAcl - IpAccessList represented by this CanonicalAcl with lines containing undefined refs and cycles sanitized to have match condition FalseExpr
        acl - IpAccessList represented by this CanonicalAcl
        dependencies - Map of names to IpAccessLists of ACLs upon which this ACL depends
        interfaces - Set of interface names of all interfaces referenced by this ACL
        linesWithUndefinedRefs - Set of line numbers of lines that refer to undefined ACLs
        linesInCycles - Set of line numbers of lines that make circular references to another ACL
